{"tid":186363,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4 Pro Club D1隊 招長打老手中後場","createTime":"2017-04-04T06:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T13:21:45.000Z","uid":76733,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ecac0124168ac5a46df5a77c8ad1fade0f97b93","tid":186363,"uid":76733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:55:38.000Z","msg":"暫時喺D1都未降過班，打左四十季拎過十一次D1 title，今屆VPL入左銀盃四強 <br />\n<br />\n我地主打4231 or 4321 三個CM LF RF，地面進攻同淫亂走位為主，類此tiki taka，較少玩燒味波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現有1 any ST,1LF,1RF,2 box to box CM,1LB,1CB<br />\n<br />\n時間 : 每星期打三四日， 21:30 - 01:00（可早開或打到訓），星期六日可能睇波未必會打<br />\n<br />\n我地誠招實而不華有經驗老手, 唔收part time, 主要係後防所有位置(除左龍門)，以及防中 or Box to Box中中（良好企/走位意識同防守技術，同埋以團隊為先)<br />\n<br />\n有興趣試腳者可以pm telegram : miroslavk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f7cceb6f4eec90b0e693464b57a761e1ec8121","tid":186363,"uid":76733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79308689ab89835a8816f67dc459eb2605a16cf1","tid":186363,"uid":79653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac60db56476f887073475772481b818ab052b87","tid":186363,"uid":71230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T11:13:09.000Z","msg":"十卜巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1bf6b206b2d4672bc02e5e34436f89b80969bd","tid":186363,"uid":71230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:47:06.000Z","msg":"勁隊！幫你推下"},{"pid":"dda630a2c319a00aa637bbb5dbd40a4e371e5